    Daydreaming
    Until quite recently most people hold a hostile attitude towards daydreaming.
They view it not only as an escape from duties and responsibilities,but also a 
sheer waste of time.
    Recent research,however,shous that daydreaming is of great banefit in many
respects.Daydreaming,scientists tell us,is a good means of active relaxation.
Surprisingly enough,it also improves our ability of getting along with others.
The most remarkable thing about daydreaming is that it is useful for shaping
our future life as we dream to be.If you always hold an ideal selfimage in your
mind,you will most probably see it come true step by step.
    Now that we can draw the conclusion that daydreaming is most beneficial,why
not make good use of it to make life rich and rewarding ?